obj_root_law_sections_15_content:
  string
  line `[Repeal of Act XLVIII of 1920.] Rep. by the Repealing and Amending Act, 1950 (35 of 1950),`
  line `s. 2 and the Schedule.`
obj_root_law_sections_15_footnotes:
  string
  line
